metadata.name: Blue Eyes&Cigarette
metadata.description:
Title : Blue Eyes&Cigarette


This work is a projection of me, who was sensitive and tired when there was a depressing event.

So there is the word 'Blue' in the name and work,
I tried to express the feeling of wanting to smoke when it was so hard.
Also, the character in the work is a character inspired by the painter I love, Vincent Van Gogh,
That's why her hair is also red, and if you look closely, she has a perforated tattoo on her ear.

I hope that my work will provide a little comfort to those who are depressed when they are having a hard time.

Created by Vinxent  30 / 04 / 2022

The collector will get
 the original PNG file in 1636 * 2334 pixel.
